    {
      "text": "Indexed\nfolder 90 - 045\n34\n\nthis but rather that,\" so that he surpasses himself in + at each new stage. (\"Nicht diese Tone; sondern...,\" as Beethoven wrote; the foundation of creation is to choose, to reject, to choose again: Boehme's dialectic ceaselessly at work, blinking off-on-off-on). Dio: creativity begins with an unvoiced no, not a yes. \"Not that; [but rather] this.\" A rejection of the is in favor of a better alternative (that is as much constructed as chosen - perhaps more so!). The esse",
